'''Bob-Manuel Obidimma Udokwu''' (yin jiji to azan fọtọ̀n-nukunatọ̀n Lidosun 1968) yin Aihundatọ, Anadena aihuntọ, Aihun basitọ po Tohodọtọ dé po to [[Naijilia]]. To 2014, eyin gigopana na azọn he e ko wa lẹ to nuwiwa he yin ''Africa Movie Academy Awards'' aotọ whenu bo yin nina gigopanamẹnu de. Ṣìgba jẹnukọnna enẹ eko yin yẹyi dogona to 2013 to aihun he eda hẹ aihungbẹ etọn dé mẹ, bo to Nollywood Movies Awards whenu eyi gigopanamẹnu lọ, aihun he mẹ e wazọn te taun lọ wẹ Adesuwa.

==Gbẹzan etọn==
Bob-Manuel Udokwu wa sọn Nkwelle-Ogidi, to pọnla Idemmili North tọn mẹ to Ayimatẹn Anambra tọn, to Otògbo Nigeria tọn mẹ. Akọta Igbo tọn mẹ wẹ e wa sọn. Otọ etọn nọ yin Geoffrey Nwafor Udokwu bọ onọ̀ etọn nọ yin Ezelagbo Udokwu. Ayimatẹn Enugu tọn wẹ e yin jiji do. Eyin ovi ẹnẹtọ to ovi ṣidopo he otọ etọn ji lẹ mẹ bo sọ yin ovi sunnu awetọ. Ovi sunnu atọn po viyọnnu awe po wẹ to whẹndo ye tọn mẹ.

==Wehihia etọn==
E yi wehọmẹ bẹjẹeji tọn ''St. Peters Primary School'' (todin Hillside Primary School) to Coal Camp, Enugu, Ayimatẹn Enugu tọn bo yí ''Oraukwu Grammar School'', to Oraukwu, Ayimatẹn Anambra tọn na wehọmẹ daho etọn. Enẹgodo e yi wehọmẹ Alavọ tọn ''University of Port Harcourt'', to Port Harcourt, Ayimatẹn Rivers tọn fi he eyi Gbedewema ''Bachelors of Arts Degree the to Theatre Arts'' mẹ. 

== Gbẹzan mẹdetiti tọn==
Udokwu mọ mẹ he wa lẹzun asi etọn he nọ yin   Cassandra Joseph to whenuena e to we hia dogọ na yí gbedewema daho etọn to Wehọmẹ Alavọ Ayimatẹ̀n Awọnlin tọn. Enẹgodo yé wlealọ to Azan koewhedopotọ Afínplọsun owhe 2000 tọn. Ye jívi awe, yọnnu lọ nọ yin Elyon Chinaza po sunnu po he nọ yin Marcus Garvey. E do Garvey Udokwu na visunnu etọn na ogan tonudido gbẹ tọn ye tọn nọ yin Marcus Garvey wutu.

